Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,请问一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这里离环球影业近吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We are close to Universal Studios?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿离这儿十英里远呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}It's about ten miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你第一次按铃我就听见了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I heard you the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,预定了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Reservations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的旅馆对我们来说不太合适\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}For us, uh, your hotel is not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以把订金还给我们吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You will please give us back our deposit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不能退款\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No refunds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们需要这笔钱去找另一家旅馆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}But we need the money for a new hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到美利坚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Welcome to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们已经预付了一晚房费\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Look, you've already paid for one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会爱上这个地方的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}This place will grow on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了问您无线网密码是多少了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Um, I-I forgot to ask you the password for Wi-Fi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有那种东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We don't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 整栋大楼都没有手机信号\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}In fact, this whole building is a dead zone for cell service.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,为了方便起见每个房间里有一部电话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}There is a telephone in each room for your convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,本地通话免费\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Local calls are free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,弄丢房门钥匙要赔偿五十美金\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}$50 fee for losing your keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么需要我帮忙的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Anything else I can help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有冰块吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,制冰机在左边第二个走廊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Ice machine is down the second hallway to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,请自便\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Knock yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,51号房发生了可怕的意外 太吓人了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Terrible accident in room 51; just ghastly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,前台\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Front desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要换房\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We must change rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这间房里有股难闻的味道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}There's a terrible smell in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们旅馆是有点发霉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}It's a musty hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,试试把空调风力开大一点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Try running the air conditioner on high.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:05:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 你必须给我们换一间房\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No, you must give us another room!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,房间都被订完了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We're sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没有空房\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Nothing available.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那人是谁 那是什么东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Who was that?! What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 我和你们一样害怕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Honey, I'm just as upset as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你们知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}And I want you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不用付那间房的房费了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}you will not be charged for that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这鬼地方我一秒钟也待不下去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I cannot stay in this place one more second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,警察一会就会过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}The police will be coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要么你们在这儿录口供\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You can either give them a statement here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要么一会儿你们因为躲避警察\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}or you can talk to them later in jail
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,被抓到监狱里去和他们说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}when they arrest you for evasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我去把你的行李拿过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'll get your bags ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以待在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}you can stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说没有空房了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I thought you said it was no other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这间房我们从来都不租出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}This one we never rent out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,拨号失败\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Your call cannot be completed as dialed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,请核对后再拨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Please check the number and dial again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,阿吉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Aggie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们认为犯罪嫌疑人从管家手里偷来钥匙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}So, we think our guy lifted the master key from housekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有人听到什么吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Nobody heard anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来两位受害者一走进房门\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Looks like both victims were chloroformed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就被氯仿麻醉了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}the second they walked through the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,让屋里亮起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Let's get some light in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,男性受害者的眼球在烟灰缸里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Male victim's eyeballs are in the ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还有他的舌头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}And his tongue?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在生不如死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}He's in a world of hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,放我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Get me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰 这片区域已经记录过了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}John, this area's been documented already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没看过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Not by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都是已婚 不过和对方不是夫妻关系\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}They were married, but not to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他们当时在偷情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}They were cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,也许被惹怒的配偶作案\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Very pissed-off spouse, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这不是情杀\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No, this isn't jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有别的动机\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}This is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手要表达的意思是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}The killer's saying the families
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的家人被蒙在鼓里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}are blind to what's been going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,放我出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Get me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会放你出去的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We're gonna get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是这么说的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}That's not what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他说的是 让我从她里面出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}He's saying, "Get me out of her."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他还在她身体里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}He's still inside of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你会在他体内\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You're gonna find
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,发现壮阳药 或许有很多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}male potency drugs in his system; probably a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在没办法把他们分开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You won't be able to detach them here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你不得不把尸体和他一并带走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}so you're gonna have to take him with the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,给他松开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Cut him loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你帮我拿到报告了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You have that report for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,法医还在现场调查\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Forensics is still on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我说的不是今早的杀人案\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No, not from the homicide this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的是上个月的马丁·甘博阿的案子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}From the Martin Gamboa case, last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,受害者叫 马丁·甘博阿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}The victim's name-- Martin Gamboa,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,四十七岁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}age 47.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,职业为奥斯卡博客作家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Profession listed as Oscar blogger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,187号案子发生在位于银湖区的死者家中\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}187 occurred in victim's home in Silver Lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,受害者死于头部钝器重击\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Victim died from blunt force trauma to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,手臂和胸部也有伤口\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}There's evidence of wounds on arms
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有些是防卫所致\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}and thorax; some defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手一开始想要折磨他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Whoever did this wanted him to suffer first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,右臂的桡骨和尺骨骨折\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Fractures to the radius and the ulna of the right arm;
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,右臂肱骨开放性骨折\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}compound fractures of the humerus of the left arm
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,骨头穿过皮肤突出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}with bone protrusions through the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在直肠腔和头盖骨里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}There are traces of what appear to be gold paint chips
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,貌似有一些金漆碎片残留\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}in the rectal cavity as well as in what is left of the cranium,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以可以猜测不管凶器是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}so it may be assumed that whatever the murder weapon was,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它还被用作性侵犯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}was also used in the sexual assault...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 爸爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Hi, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,学校怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}How was school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 莉兹·库珀在拼写时\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Good. Lizzy Cooper threw up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,紧张到呕吐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}in the middle of spelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然挺恶心的 但也很有趣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}It was gross and awesome at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,男孩们现在都叫他莉兹·呕吐怪了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}The boys are calling her Lizzy Puker now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈呢 她想和我说几句吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}How's Mom? Does she want to talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 妈妈 你要和爸爸打个招呼吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Hey, Mom, do you want to say hi to Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不了 亲爱的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃饭了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了 骗子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Yes. Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 你准备好讲故事了吗 快到睡觉时间了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}All right, you ready to read? It's almost bedtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,洛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Lowe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,三号线上有你的电话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You got a call on line three.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我留言\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Take a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他很执着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Uh, he was pretty adamant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 你去忙吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Daddy, you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要讲睡前故事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We read at bedtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谁先来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Who's gonna start?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,男孩们已经耗尽了所有耐心 天知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}"Boys are trying enough to human patience, goodness knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但女孩们绝对更为...”\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}"But girls are infinitely more so..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你能前后对照一下甘博阿和\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Can you cross-reference the Gamboa forensics
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,旅馆案件的取证吗 比如指纹什么的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}with the hotel case-- prints, everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 约翰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Hello, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不接我的电话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Why didn't you take my call?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会有我的号码\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}How'd you get this number?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我把他们钉到床头板上了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I nailed them to the headboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我在科尔特兹旅馆的64号房\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm at the Hotel Cortez, room 64.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我将会旧戏重演\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm going to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我要一间房 就住一晚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I need a room, one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一百五十美元\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}150.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这里说是三十美元 这个是以前的价格\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35} It says here 30.  It's out of date.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,重新装修后涨价了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Prices went up after the remodel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你在扯淡吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Okay, well, that's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,今天算你走运\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}It's your lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老娘今天宽宏大量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Mama's feeling magnanimous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,64号房\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Room 64.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 电梯今天不能用了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh, elevator's out of service today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我先要了 艾丽斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I got dibs on this one, Iris.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没见过这样的鲜肉了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I haven't seen one that sweet in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,人一死 就会弄脏床单\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}When people die, they soil the sheets--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,血啊 屎啊 尿啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}blood, shit, urine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,任何污渍我都能清理干净\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I can take care of every stain there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哇呜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Woof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真养眼呀\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You're a sight for sore eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,警官先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Mr. Police Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有这么明显吗 嗯哼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}-It's that obvious, huh? -Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定经常和警察打交道吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You must have a lot of run-ins with police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还行吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}My fair share.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你能告诉我64号房住客的情况么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}What can you tell me about the occupant in room 64?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那间房是空的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}That room's vacant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你介意我上去看一眼么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You mind if I take a quick look?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,悉听尊便\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh, be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,丽兹·泰勒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Liz Taylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,带这位好警官去64号房\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Show this nice policeman to room 64.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,64号 是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}64? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,64号房\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Room 64.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,马上去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,救我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫得越大声 他就越喜欢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}The more you scream, the more he likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你能和我说说在这旅馆出入的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}What can you tell me about the people
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,都是哪些人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}that come in and out of this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大多是长期住客还是暂时住客\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}They mostly residents or transients?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 这儿什么人都有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh, we got a bit of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有的开包月房 有的开钟点房\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Some pay by the month, some pay by the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有些老前辈很久以前就住在这了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Some of the old-timers have been here since the dawn of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那你呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你要找什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Who are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,无可奉告\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Not at liberty to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我不是那个意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh, I don't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看到你眼神里的悲痛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I can see the pain in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,似曾相识的眼神\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}It's very familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 你失去了什么东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh, you've lost something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如今你卡在了时间里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}And now you're frozen in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,停滞不前了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Can't move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,也不能回头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,说你爱我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Tell me you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,说出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,说“我爱你 莎莉” 它就会消失了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Say, "I love you, Sally," And it will all go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,说啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你 莎莉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I love you, Sally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一遍\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,再说 一遍\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Say it... again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你 萨利\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I love you, Sally.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我自己进去就行了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Alright, I'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:22:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我没带现金\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I don't have any cash.
