Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.31,0:33:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Read my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.64,0:33:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我是谁啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.13,0:34:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 让我们走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Please, let us go.
