Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.62,0:34:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,让你们的伤口好得更快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}help your wounds heal faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.66,0:34:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一点鸡肝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}And we got you some chicken livers...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.99,0:34:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,肾 富含铁哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}...kidneys, packed with iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.22,0:34:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要让你们的红细胞活跃起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Get those red blood cells pumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.97,0:34:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,压轴戏来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}And to top it off,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.80,0:35:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,再加点教皇新堡葡萄酒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}a Chateauneuf-du-Pape Grenache blanc.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.26,0:35:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.18,0:35:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 拜托 不要 唔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Please. Please, don't. Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.73,0:35:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.33,0:35:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是帮助你们身体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}This is just the thing to get your bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.52,0:35:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,吸收这些营养的好东西而已\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}to absorb all these nutrients.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.85,0:35:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要 不要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Stop. Stop. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.77,0:35:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你 不要这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Don't. Please don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.61,0:35:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以自己吃 也可以等我灌你们吃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We can do this the easy way or the hard way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.94,0:35:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但我是不会离开的哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}But I'm not leaving
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.45,0:35:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,直到你们把所有维他命和矿物质都吃完\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}until you get all your vitamins and minerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.70,0:35:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你 求求你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.95,0:35:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 来吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}All right. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.12,0:35:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 谁最爱吃营养早餐啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No! No! No! Breakfast of champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.43,0:35:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,张开嘴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Open your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.04,0:35:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要这么残忍吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Do you really need to be so aggressive?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.59,0:35:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不能有点怜悯之心吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Can't you have some compassion?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.05,0:35:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我滚出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.06,0:35:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你从来不顾这些女孩死活的 那你就在乎吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You don't give a shit about these girls. And you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.56,0:35:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你的关心是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I've seen what your caring looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.14,0:35:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们大家心知肚明\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We've all seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.78,0:35:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我有关心的人和事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}At least I care about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.86,0:36:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我想在这里吗 周围都是瘾君子和腐朽的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Think I want to be here, surrounded by junkies and decay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.32,0:36:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 那你为什么不离开呢 走啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Well, then why don't you leave? Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.12,0:36:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你这二十年来一直在抱怨同一件事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You've been whining about the same thing for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.66,0:36:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你不停地逼逼啊逼逼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You talk a good talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.16,0:36:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你从没离开过 因为事实就是你爱死这里了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}but you stick around because the truth is you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.71,0:36:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.83,0:36:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,让我困在这个肮脏的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm stuck in this godforsaken cesspool
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.25,0:36:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,充满痛苦的沼泽的罪魁祸首就是你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}of pain and shit 'cause of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.92,0:36:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,额\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.17,0:36:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是我痛苦的根源\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You're the beginning and the end
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.67,0:36:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,和结尾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}of all my suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.92,0:36:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.10,0:36:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Well, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.15,0:36:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,受够了这个烂摊子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Done with your bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.68,0:36:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,受够这里了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Done with it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.52,0:36:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为你自己比我做得好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You think you can do this better?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.27,0:36:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那你自己来吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Then you do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.39,0:36:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但你最好能把这工作做好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}But you better do a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.50,0:36:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不然你自己去跟她解释 为什么她们还是这种味道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Otherwise you can explain to her why they still taste like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.87,0:36:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我去喂33号房的那个东西了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I got to go feed that thing in room 33.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.25,0:36:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.01,0:36:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.37,0:37:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.46,0:37:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.43,0:37:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道这间房子以前是干什么的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Do you know what this room used to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.44,0:37:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是用来演木偶戏的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}This old dude used to put on a puppet show right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.86,0:37:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,提线木偶人 用线穿着 供大家消遣娱乐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Marionettes, strings, for entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.23,0:37:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,而你们现在呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}And now you...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.70,0:37:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要来供我消遣娱乐了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}...are going to entertain me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.99,0:37:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,用你们的眼泪感动我吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Move me with your tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.88,0:37:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,跑吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.58,0:37:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,跑啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.81,0:38:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 糟了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.06,0:38:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道怎么回事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.03,0:38:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她不知怎的逃了出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}She got loose somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.06,0:38:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事情不允许再发生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}This can never happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.20,0:39:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该问问这些是不是日本的鱼肉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Shouldn't we ask if any of this fish is from Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.79,0:39:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.41,0:39:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有辐射啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.12,0:39:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你真像你的妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You're starting to sound like your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.95,0:39:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她总说小心一点是没错的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}She always said she had a good reason to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.30,0:39:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨晚又梦到他了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I had a dream about him again last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.75,0:39:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我没办法再看清他的脸了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I can't see his face anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.80,0:39:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有在梦里才能想起那张脸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I can't remember it except in my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.76,0:39:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那样我才能看见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}then I can really see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.18,0:39:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我一醒来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}When I wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.23,0:39:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我就记不清了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.68,0:39:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒来后还记得他的样子吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Do you remember what he looks like when you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.44,0:39:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.09,0:39:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们应该把照片重新挂出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Maybe we should put the pictures up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.58,0:40:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,饭桌上不要玩手机\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No electronics at the dinner table.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.54,0:40:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}It's your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.13,0:40:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是亚利克斯 请留言\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You've reached Alex, please leave a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.02,0:40:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 怎么了 进去看了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Dad, what's happening?! Been inside yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.97,0:40:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 我才到 怎么了 警探\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No, I just got here. What's going on, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.64,0:40:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还不知道 看着我女儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I don't know yet. Watch my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.98,0:41:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,亚历克斯 你还好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Alex, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.91,0:41:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰·洛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}John Lowe.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.38,0:41:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.83,0:41:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我妻子呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Where's my wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.25,0:41:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过我会再干一次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I told you I'd do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.76,0:41:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,把手举起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Show me your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.81,0:42:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,站住\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.95,0:42:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,站住\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.44,0:42:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,斯嘉丽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Scarlett!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.74,0:43:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 亲爱的 你瞄准了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}All right, honey, you got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.27,0:43:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 差一点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh, so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.78,0:43:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我带霍顿去坐旋转木马\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm gonna take Holden to the carousel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.17,0:43:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 宝贝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}All right, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.56,0:43:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 伙计\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Come on, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.77,0:43:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,慢点来 慢点来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Slow it down, slow it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.34,0:43:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,记住像拿铅笔一样握住\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Remember, hold it like a pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.28,0:43:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,然后像扔棒球一样扔出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Throw it like a baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.73,0:43:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄准目标\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Concentrate on where you want it to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.11,0:43:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好了吗 开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Ready? Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.45,0:43:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 你真棒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.49,0:43:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你饿了吗 伙计\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You hungry, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.07,0:43:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我想吃棉花糖\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Yeah, I want some cotton candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.41,0:43:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,饿了要吃正餐的啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You got to eat some real food first.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.41,0:43:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没有那么饿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm not hungry for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.88,0:43:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 那骑完之后再去吃东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No? All right, we'll get something after.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.67,0:43:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.76,0:43:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这个马脚是黄色的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You got one with yellow feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.56,0:43:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很特别哟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}He's a special one.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.65,0:44:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,霍顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Holden?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.13,0:44:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见我儿子了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Hey, you seen my boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.63,0:44:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他坐在黄脚的木马上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}He was on that horse with the yellow feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.30,0:44:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,霍顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Holden!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.47,0:44:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,霍顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Holden!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.02,0:44:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,霍顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Holden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.97,0:44:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,霍顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Holden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.39,0:44:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,霍顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Holden!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.56,0:44:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,霍顿 霍顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Holden! Holden!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.15,0:44:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们该搬到玛丽那里去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I mean, maybe we should just go stay with Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.15,0:44:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,新罕布什尔州吗 我不想这样对斯嘉丽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}In New Hampshire? I don't want to do that to Scarlett.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.70,0:44:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经很难受了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}It's already gonna be hard enough as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.24,0:44:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她应该在自己的床上睡觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}She should be able to sleep in her own bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.87,0:44:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我会安排两名警察时刻跟着你们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm gonna have two uniformed men with you at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.38,0:44:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一个跟着斯嘉丽去上学\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}One's gonna go to school with Scarlett, one's gonna go
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.50,0:44:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一个跟着你上班 他们都很优秀\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}to work with you, and these guys are very good at what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.67,0:44:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会意识到他们跟着你的 一旦你需要帮助 他们就会出现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You're not even gonna know they are there unless you need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.42,0:45:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这个人的样子吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Do you even know what this guy looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.34,0:45:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他怎么用我的手机给你发了短信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I don't understand how he texted you from my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.09,0:45:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他知道我们住在哪里吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I mean, do you think that he knows where we live?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.01,0:45:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 约翰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Jesus, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.48,0:45:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该怎么办\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}What are we gonna do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.01,0:45:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我该买把枪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Maybe I should get a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.19,0:45:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你不需要买枪 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No. No, you-you don't need to get a gun, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.07,0:45:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定有复制手机的办法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}There are ways to clone somebody's phone, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.82,0:45:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要担心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.02,0:45:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保护你们的安全\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm gonna keep you guys safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.27,0:45:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么保护 搬出去吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}What, by moving out?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.51,0:45:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉他还会来找我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I have a feeling he's gonna come after me again,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.20,0:45:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话 我不想让你们在我身边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}and if that happens, I don't want either of you near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.91,0:45:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我不是因为你要走而伤心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Look, I'm not upset because you're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.08,0:45:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而是因为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm upset because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.09,0:45:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我想过让你离开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I secretly want you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.87,0:45:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I-I understand. You...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.59,0:45:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该把斯嘉丽带到那个房子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I shouldn't have brought Scarlett to that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.26,0:45:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你遇到了麻烦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I thought you were in trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.63,0:45:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫那个白痴警察看着她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I-I told that idiot cop to watch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.96,0:45:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是因为那个生气\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm not mad about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.05,0:45:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不会让她受到伤害\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I know you would never put her in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.39,0:45:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,霍顿的事情 我也不怪你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}And I don't blame you for Holden.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.19,0:45:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你是怎么想的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No matter what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.14,0:46:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我很爱你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.18,0:46:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他和你长得太像了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}He looks just so much like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.37,0:46:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天看着你 就像看到了他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I see him in your face
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.03,0:46:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨不得去死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}every day and I just want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.31,0:46:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这不公平 他们抢走了我的儿子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}It's not fair-- they took my little boy from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.79,0:46:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我却甚至不能正眼看着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}and I can't even look at the one person in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.57,0:46:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这世上唯一了解我感受的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}who understands how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.21,0:46:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是需要远离这一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I just need a break from it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.16,0:46:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你有过希望吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Do you ever hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.88,0:46:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都在希望着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I can't stop hoping.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.72,0:46:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那才是最难受的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}That's the worst part.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.83,0:46:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.70,0:46:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,雨停了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}The rain may have stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.95,0:46:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但今天还是阴天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}but it's still a gloomy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.95,0:46:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不把我的狗送去安乐死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I had to put my dog down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.04,0:47:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他在不幸的处境时找上了我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}He came to me through very unfortunate circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.17,0:47:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们不会想听的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}But you don't need to hear about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.54,0:47:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这边走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.02,0:47:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的建筑物都是历史遗迹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}So many buildings around here are time capsules,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.97,0:47:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,由非个人的企业信托所保管\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}locked away by an impersonal business trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.80,0:47:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢和信托打交道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I prefer dealing with a trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.30,0:47:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,匿名而且实事求是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Anonymous. Unsentimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.19,0:47:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是来这里住 还是来这里工作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}So you'll live here, or just work here?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.78,0:47:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你对顶楼很感兴趣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I know that you were interested in the top floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.86,0:47:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们全搬过来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We're moving our life out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.48,0:47:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法区分工作与家庭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Work, home-- I've never kept them separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.61,0:47:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说很明确 洛杉矶曾是艺术的天堂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}It's very clear to me: the art world has looked to L.A.,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.65,0:47:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,潮流会紧随而来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}and fashion is soon to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.98,0:47:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我会住在顶楼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}The top floor is where I'll live
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.58,0:47:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,下面就是现成的工作室\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}and just below will be an atelier, mostly ready-to-wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.16,0:47:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,拉克伦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Lachlan!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.62,0:47:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,拉克伦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Lachlan!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.16,0:47:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,拉克伦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Lachlan?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.33,0:47:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.66,0:47:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他真是活泼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}So much energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.33,0:47:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么需要帮忙的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.15,0:47:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,额 我是卖房子的地产经纪人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Uh, I'm the realtor
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.50,0:47:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我来带他们看房子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}representing the sale. We're here for the walk-through.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.17,0:47:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有需要会告诉你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We'll let you know if we need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.47,0:47:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,卖房子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Sale?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.76,0:47:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,什么卖房子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}What sale?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.06,0:47:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Well, I know it was
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.56,0:47:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事还没公开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}a whisper listing, but surely,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.00,0:48:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但房主肯定告诉了你吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}the owner should have told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.35,0:48:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没人他妈的告诉我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Nobody tells me shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.02,0:48:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我连房主都没见过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I've never even met the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.57,0:48:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那你现在见到了 亲爱的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Well, you have now, dearie.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.02,0:48:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这是新房主威尔·德雷克先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}This is the new owner, Mr. Will Drake.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.74,0:48:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先看顶层的套房吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We'll start with the penthouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.94,0:48:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有需要会告诉你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We'll let you know if we need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.19,0:48:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去睡大街了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We're gonna be turned out onto the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.15,0:48:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,云已经散开了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}The clouds have cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.91,0:49:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可以一直看到太平洋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Sightlines all the way to the Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.12,0:49:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,拉上窗帘\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Close it!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.16,0:49:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,光太亮了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}The light!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.88,0:49:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你们他妈的是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Who the hell are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.42,0:49:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在我房间里干什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}And what are you doing in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.76,0:49:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被侵入了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We've been invaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.43,0:49:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,被卖了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Shanghaied!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.30,0:49:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一个该死的纽约客在我的套房里面量尺寸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Some goddamn New Yorker is sizing up my suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.48,0:49:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这个点儿对你来说有点早了 不是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}A little early for you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.77,0:49:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你会更喜欢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I know you'll prefer the view
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.77,0:49:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚才见到的景\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}from the space we just saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.31,0:49:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但这里是这层楼的另外一半\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}but here's the other half of the floor plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.95,0:49:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了 光照问题是个挑战\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}The lighting is, of course, a challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.83,0:49:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不知道这些霓虹灯能不能起点作用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}and I don't know if all this neon is the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.61,0:49:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,威尔·德雷克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Will Drake.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.45,0:49:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你真荣幸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I am so pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.01,0:49:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你为奥巴马夫人做的那套礼服\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I was completely impressed with the gown you made
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.25,0:49:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真的让我印象深刻\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}for Mrs. Obama.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.71,0:49:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那是宴请\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}It was the state dinner for...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.42,0:49:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,西班牙领导人的国宴 没错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}The Spaniards, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.88,0:49:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,听你提起倍感荣幸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Kind of you to mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.21,0:49:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我在食疗净化\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm on a cleanse.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.47,0:49:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在开始不是了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.72,0:50:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,拉克兰 说你呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Lachlan! Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.27,0:50:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,指纹是最不容易擦掉的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Fingerprints are really hard to get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.94,0:50:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,无心之过都是可以原谅的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Messes are always forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.04,0:50:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}The first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.20,0:50:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-那是 -没错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Is... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.99,0:50:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是艾力克·李维的作品\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}It's an Arik Levy
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.57,0:50:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是我自己的藏品\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}and it doesn't come with the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.80,0:50:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了 我更希望你能像我们一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Of course, I'm hopeful you're as interested
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.08,0:50:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对科尔特兹本身感兴趣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}in the character of The Cortez as we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.33,0:50:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这里充满了能量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}There's energy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.37,0:50:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我走过无数纽约街道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I walk through New York
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.36,0:50:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而我再也没有听见过音乐声\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}streets and I don't hear the music anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.58,0:50:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,再也没有能与我产生共鸣的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No more echos of who I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.05,0:50:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,街道被重建 历史的痕迹被抹掉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Blocks are toppled, history erased,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.14,0:50:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都是怪人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}weirdoes banished.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.18,0:50:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这里简直就是另外一个世界\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}This place is far enough away
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.31,0:50:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,能与我交流\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}that it speaks to me--
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.85,0:50:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至在对我歌唱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}it sings, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.15,0:50:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经等不及\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Well, I cannot wait
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.52,0:50:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要看看你能把这里改造成什么样子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}to see what you make of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.52,0:50:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,说得真动听\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}That's really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.19,0:50:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那像我们这样的怪人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}So where are weirdoes like us
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.11,0:50:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,该住在哪儿呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}supposed to live, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.19,0:51:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有哪首歌告诉你这件事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Any songs telling you anything about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.26,0:51:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,或许你可以为我们的邻居\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Perhaps you could show our neighbor
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.96,0:51:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,展示一下詹姆斯·特瑞尔的光雕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}the James Turrell light sculpture?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.80,0:51:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 我能留下来看看这些唱片吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Dad, can I stay and look at the records?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.27,0:51:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Of course you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.97,0:51:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,人们不该住在旅馆里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}People aren't supposed to live in hotels.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.94,0:51:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,或许这里是特例\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Well, maybe this place is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.73,0:51:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我带你去一些看你会感兴趣的东西如何\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I want to show you something you'll enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.74,0:51:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一会儿就回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We'll only be gone a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.25,0:51:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我很多年前曾住在纽约\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I lived in New York, many years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.83,0:51:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢在街道上漫步\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I loved roaming the streets,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.05,0:51:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,全神贯注地感受这座城市的脉动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}devouring the pulse of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.05,0:51:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,让我很兴奋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Electrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.89,0:52:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我怀念这种感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I miss it very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.92,0:52:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在搬走的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Did your father give you a choice
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.43,0:52:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸有给过你选择吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}when it came time to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.90,0:52:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸不让我跟陌生人说话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}My dad says I'm not supposed to talk to strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.10,0:52:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是陌生人 拉克兰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We're not strangers, Lachlan.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.57,0:52:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会成为好朋友的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We're going to be great friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.24,0:52:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.74,0:52:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这走廊有什么好看的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}What's so special about a  hallway?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.74,0:53:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,霍顿 我们有客人了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Holden, we have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.46,0:53:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你的礼貌呢 小天使\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Where are your manners, angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.83,0:53:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 想一起玩吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Hello. Want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.12,0:53:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你听见了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.33,0:53:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他们卖了这栋旅馆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}They sold the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.24,0:53:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都会被遣散的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We'll be cast to the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.50,0:53:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就当这是件好事吧 妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Consider it a blessing, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.50,0:53:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你很久之前就该离开这儿了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You should have left this place years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.32,0:53:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这儿工作是因为我想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm here because I need to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.00,0:53:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都见到你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.22,0:53:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你是时候放手了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Time for you to let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.73,0:53:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,#当你孤单一个#\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}# When you're alone #
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.98,0:54:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,#而生活逼你独自面对#\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}# And life is making you lonely #
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.52,0:54:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,#你总有个去处#\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}# You can always go #
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.32,0:54:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,#市区#\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}# Downtown #
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.15,0:54:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,#当你忧心忡忡#\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}# When you've got worries #
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.61,0:54:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,#噪音与催促让你烦扰#\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}# All the noise and the hurry #
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.94,0:54:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,#我知道有个去处#\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}# Seems to help, I know #
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.44,0:54:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,#市区#\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}# Downtown #
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.03,0:54:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,#仔细聆听那音乐#\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}# Just listen to the music #
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.91,0:54:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,#来自城市的交通熙攘#\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}# Of the traffic in the city... #
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.81,0:54:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你能告诉我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Can you tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.40,0:54:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们住在哪间吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}what room they're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.62,0:54:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚走进来的那对儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}The couple that just came in?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.65,0:54:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 女士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm sorry, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.32,0:54:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是保密旅馆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}This is a no-tell motel.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.48,0:54:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男孩是我儿子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}That boy is my son
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.46,0:55:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而那个瘾君子打算让他吸毒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}and that junkie's about to give him dope.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.16,0:55:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,给\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.47,0:55:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 别这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.84,0:55:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,最近的提款机在哪里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Where's the nearest ATM?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.62,0:55:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在药店里的拐角处\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}At the corner drugstore,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.92,0:55:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,挨着卫生巾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}right next to the maxi pads.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.76,0:55:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 兄弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.77,0:55:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Goddamn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.44,0:55:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.00,0:55:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.80,0:55:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我一个新针头 行吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You're gonna give me a fresh needle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.61,0:55:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你认识的最健康的人了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm the cleanest person you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.98,0:56:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,来啦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.94,0:56:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你给他用了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}What'd you give him?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.11,0:56:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,多诺万\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Donovan?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.19,0:57:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他不省人事了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}He's out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.94,0:57:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谁让你进来的 女士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Who invited you in, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.91,0:57:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底给他用了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}What did you give him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.28,0:57:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,中国白粉啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}China White.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.38,0:57:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经去了他想要去的地方了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Which means he is just where he wants to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.43,0:57:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,报警啊 报警干嘛呀\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Call 911! No one's calling anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.62,0:57:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,快醒醒 我告诉过他让他悠着点别学我的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Come on... I told him not to try and keep up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.79,0:57:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们用量一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We took the same shit
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.42,0:57:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,而我这不还好好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}and I am more than fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.76,0:57:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,至少在你闯进来之前我还好好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}At least until you barged in.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.05,0:57:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You can't leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.06,0:57:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 拜托\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.30,0:57:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我买这白粉花了多少钱吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}You know how much I paid for this dope?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.47,0:57:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.47,0:57:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.61,0:57:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.56,0:58:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.36,0:58:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你儿子的下巴我喜欢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Your boy has a jawline for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.96,0:59:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,# On a dark desert highway #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.25,0:59:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,# Cool wind in my hair #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.42,0:59:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,# Warm smell of colitas #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.59,0:59:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,# Rising up through the air #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.59,0:59:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,# Up ahead in the distance #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.93,0:59:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,# I saw a shimmering light #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.23,0:59:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,# My head grew heavy and my sight grew dim #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.57,0:59:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,# I had to stop for the night #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.10,0:59:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,# There she stood in the doorway #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.94,0:59:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,# I heard the mission bell #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.28,0:59:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,# And I was thinking to myself #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.44,0:59:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,# This could be heaven #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.11,0:59:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,# Or this could be hell #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.75,0:59:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,# Then she lit up her candle #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.12,0:59:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,# And she showed me the way #
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.54,1:00:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,# There were voices down the corridor #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.29,1:00:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,# Thought I heard them say #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.60,1:00:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,# Such a lovely place #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.55,1:00:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,# Such a lovely place #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.97,1:00:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,# Such a lovely face #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.72,1:00:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,# They livin' it up at the Hotel California #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.81,1:00:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,# What a nice surprise #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.65,1:00:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,# What a nice surprise #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.40,1:00:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,# Bring your alibis #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.24,1:00:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,# Mirrors on the ceiling #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.32,1:00:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,# The pink champagne on ice #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.66,1:00:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,# And she said, we are all just prisoners here #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.66,1:00:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,# Of our own device #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.67,1:00:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,# And in the master's chambers #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.14,1:00:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,# They gathered for the feast #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.26,1:00:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,# They stab it with their steely knives #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.76,1:00:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,# But they just can't kill the beast #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.76,1:00:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,# Last thing I remember #
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.52,1:01:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,# I was running for the door #
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.19,1:01:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,# I had to find the passage back #
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.19,1:01:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,# To the place I was before #
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.19,1:01:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,# Relax, said the night man #
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.36,1:01:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,# We are programmed to receive #
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.61,1:01:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,# You can check out any time you like #
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.52,1:01:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,# But you can never leave... #
